 <body ><br><h1 class="pHead1" >
assert_never_unknown
</h1>    
<a name="wp3769087"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that the value of a specified expression contains only 0 and 1 bits when a qualifying expression is TRUE.  </p>    <div align="left" class="tbl">
