  <h4 class="pHead4" >
</h4>    

<a name="wp3773990"> </a><h3 class="pHead3" >
Notes
</h3>    

<a name="wp3773991"> </a><p class="pNumber" >
 1.	If &#8216;OVL_XCHECK_OFF is set, all <code class="cCodeBody">assert_never_unknown</code> checkers are turned off.
</p>    
